      <title>美国称 Meta 呼吁禁止 FTC 修改隐私协议是不恰当的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/meta-bid-to-bar-ftc-from-changing-privacy-pact-improper-us-says</link>
