    <item>
      <title>Meta 在应用程序中测试新的人工智能功能以提高吸引力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/meta-tests-new-ai-features-across-facebook-instagram-to-boost-apps-appeal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 押注人工智能明年将说服人们在其社交媒体应用上花费更多时间，并利用该技术在其平台上做出自 2020 年推出短视频 Reels 以来最大的改变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/meta-tests-new-ai-features-across-facebook-instagram-to-boost-apps-appeal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 17:00:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麦当劳求助于 Google 人工智能聊天机器人来帮助餐厅员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/mcdonald-s-mcd-getting-ai-chatbot-from-google-googl-for-restaurant-crew</link>
      <description><![CDATA[麦当劳公司正在向 Alphabet Inc. 旗下的谷歌寻求帮助，打造一款聊天机器人，帮助其餐厅员工快速获得诸如如何清洁冰淇淋机等问题的答案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/mcdonald-s-mcd-getting-ai-chatbot-from-google-googl-for-restaurant-crew</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 16:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊针对 Shein 降低廉价服装卖家的费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/amazon-targets-shein-with-big-fee-cuts-for-cheap-apparel-sellers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司正在大幅削减销售价格低于 20 美元服装的商家的费用，这表明该公司准备与中国快时尚新贵 Shein 展开价格战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/amazon-targets-shein-with-big-fee-cuts-for-cheap-apparel-sellers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 02:07:29 GMT</pubDate>
